      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/png;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" /\r\nalt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eAR-AP Cashflow Forecasting\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThe AR-AP Cashflow Forecasting App is an AI-powered solution designed to provide business users with accurate and actionable insights into their cash inflows (Accounts Receivable) and outflows (Accounts Payable). By utilizing advanced machine learning algorithms like Sarimax and Prophet, this app offers precise forecasting that helps businesses better manage liquidity, ensure financial stability, and proactively address potential cashflow issues.\r\n                 \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eBusiness users upload AR, AP, or Payroll data, select the model type, and define the forecast period for prediction and scenario analysis.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n             \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThe app generates accurate 12-month forecasts for receivables, payables, and payroll; visualizes trends and seasonality; highlights anomalies; and supports strategic decisions through model comparisons and scenario outcomes.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n             \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \r\n   \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eAI-Based Forecasting: Uses SARIMAX for trends and external drivers, Prophet for seasonality, holidays, and non-linear patterns.Select cashflow type (AR, AP, or Payroll)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eReal-Time Updates: Keeps forecasts aligned with current business data such as invoices and payment schedules.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eScenario Simulation: Helps visualize financial impact of changes in payment terms, behavior, or business assumptions.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eStrategic Planning Support: Provides long-term visibility for confident decision-making and growth planning.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n               \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
